SPACE can also be decorated with NFTs that you will find in game. You can connect multiple SPACE together to customize the layout of your Personal Metaverse. A Small Exalted SPACE has 3 Exits that can be used to connect to other SPACE or Utility NFTs.

SPACE can also be decorated with NFTs that you will find in game. You can connect multiple SPACE together to customize the layout of your Personal Metaverse. A Small Exalted SPACE has 3 Exits that can be used to connect to other SPACE or Utility NFTs.

game.name: Big Time
game.description: Big Time is a free-to-play, multiplayer action RPG game that combines fast-action combat and adventure through time and space.
